FBIS4-38236 "drnes125_c_94009" FBIS-NES-94-125 Daily Report 28 Jun 1994 Egypt Prominent Islamic Lawyer Detained Prominent Islamic Lawyer Detained NC2806180394 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1710 GMT 28 Jun 94 NC2806180394 Cairo MENA Arabic BFN [Text] Cairo, 28 Jun (MENA)--The Higher State Security Prosecution today decided to detain Lawyer Muntassir al-Zayyat for 15 days of interrogation under the supervision of the Prosecution. The security department had referred al-Zayyat to the State Security Prosecution for interrogation about charges that he belongs to an extremist religious group. Al-Zayyat is considered one of the most prominent lawyers defending the extremist Islamic groups in Egypt.
